              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a professional nutritionist.\nCalculate total calories for all meals combined.\nEstimate total Proteins, Fats, and Carbohydrates for the entire day.\""
            },
            {
              "content": "=Below is a list of ALL meals consumed by the user today. Please sum these up and provide one single analysis for the entire day\n\nMeals:\n{{ $json.meal_items }}\n{{ $json.meal_calories }}\n\nEach object in the array has these fields:\n- meal_items: array of strings, food items in the meal\n- meal_calories: number, calories in the meal\n\nTasks:\n1. Calculate total calories for all meals combined.\n2. Estimate total Proteins (g), Fats (g), and Carbohydrates (g).\n3. Assess the balance of the diet.\n4. Provide 3 clear suggestions to improve nutrition.\n\nReturn ONLY JSON in this format:\n\n{\n  \"total_calories\": 0,\n  \"proteins_g\": 0,\n  \"fats_g\": 0,\n  \"carbs_g\": 0,\n  \"analysis\": \"\",\n  \"suggestions\": []\n}\n"
            }
